videos.description: Marc Gosselin gets the steal and passes ahead to Amir Coffey who gets the layup and-1.
videos.headline: Minnesota scores on fastbreak steal

videos.description: Minnesota spreads the ball around until it finds Reggie Lynch who throws down the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Great ball movement leads to Golden Gophers' dunk

videos.description: Davonte Fitzgerald grabs the offensive rebound off his own missed shot and hits the ensuing jumper.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Fitzgerald scores off own miss

videos.description: Nate Mason drives to the bucket and finds Bakary Konate wide open who makes the easy dunk.
videos.headline: Golden Gophers connect under the basket for dunk

videos.description: Amir Coffey gets the steal and passes ahead to Dupree McBrayer who makes the great behind-the-back pass back to Coffey for the dunk.
videos.headline: Behind-the-back pass leads to Minnesota dunk

videos.description: Isaiah Washington has the ball poked away from him but hangs on to get the layup high off the glass.
videos.headline: Loose ball leads to acrobatic Minnesota layup

videos.description: Jordan Murphy grabs the offensive board and fights off contact for the dunk plus the foul.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Murphy gets the putback dunk and-1

videos.description: Minnesota's Nate Mason goes in for the drive and tosses it to Bakary Konate who finishes strong with a dunk.

videos.description: Golden Gophers' Dupree McBrayer bounce passes it backwards to Amir Coffey who jams it in for a dunk.

videos.description: Golden Gophers' Isaiah Washington goes into drive and take a shot, and Catamounts' Mike Amius takes a swat at the ball, but the ball still goes in the net.
